    "Experimental profile. Keep required top-level blocks: profile_name, profile_version, claim_types, claim_type_aliases, mutually_exclusive_categories, claim_type_override_rules, normalization_rules.",
    "Hint lists are intentionally capped and curated. Add high-value recurring terms only; avoid vague words that cause broad false matches.",
    "Pose vocabulary is SFW and descriptive. Do not add explicit sexual anatomy or graphic sexual acts."
  ],
  "_editing_warnings": [
    "Rules are evaluated in order. More specific rules should remain before broad rules.",
    "Aliases must point to claim types listed in claim_types.",
    "color_noun rules should generally inspect normalized text to avoid unrelated original-claim words stealing category assignment.",
    "visible_text should generally inspect normalized text so garments/props are not mislabeled as text unless the normalized claim preserves readable text."
